            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[# DingDone 1.0.3

## New

- DingDone now detects Codex hooks that still need approval and guides you to the correct settings.

## Improved

- Hosted voice previews are cached locally for faster repeat playback.
- Per-project voice selection is available again.
- The widget attention indicator now stays attached to the mascot.

## Fixed

- ElevenLabs connection status stays “Not checked” while a key is being entered and changes to “Connected” only after successful verification.
]]></description>
