            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>13.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[# DingDone 1.0.0

The first public release of DingDone.

## What's new

- Voice notifications when Claude Code and Codex finish work, need an answer, or continue working.
- Offline speech using macOS system voices, with language, voice, phrase, and per-project settings.
- A menu-bar panel with recent events, quick sound controls, and navigation to the relevant project or session.
- Agent Cockpit: a floating widget and a list of sessions that need attention.
- A library of additional voices and secure DingDone Pro activation.

## Reliability and privacy

- Agent hooks call a separate CLI, so notifications continue to work when the DingDone window is closed.
- Free mode with system voices works locally and does not require an account.
- Full agent message contents are not written to the event log.
]]></description>
